DJ Cuppy has reacted to her sister, Temi Otedola’s engagement to her boyfriend, Mr Eazi. DAILY POST had reported that Mr. Eazi engaged his girlfriend, Temi Otedola, daughter of Femi Otedola. Temi made the announcement on her Twitter page on Sunday. The daughter of the business mogul posted a video of the proposal in London. Reacting, DJ Cuppy congratulated the couple and revealed that she introduced the duo. “OMG OMG OMG! My sister is getting married. “Today is one of the happiest days of my life. Thank you @MrEazi for bringing such joy to our family! “Congratulations to my favourite couple on their engagement! I’m so happy that my lil sister @TemiOtedola has found her personal person! Yo @MrEazi I’ve always wanted an older brother, Welcome to the family! “PS: I introduced you guys, so you better find me my own o.”